# help(true)) :- ...` is FIVE separate Prolog
# clauses (one per option) that match on the
# COMPOUND TERM SHAPE arriving from
# `opt_arguments/3`.  Each parsed option becomes
# `OptName(Value)` (e.g. `help(true)`,
